summary: Pack up your stuff, its time to move out of that old cave.
descriptionHtml:
Pack up your stuff, its time to move out of that old cave. Situated high up in the mountains northwest of Bleak Falls Barrow and just shy west of Whiterun makes this home a ideal location. With its beautiful valley view and great set up, this player home is a good choice. 

All containers are custom, meaning I just didn\'t slap 10 chests on the ground and said heres your storage. I custom made everyone. It has a great shop and a nice lab. I added a teleportation system to and from all major holds and its on the map. Hall of Valor is still under contruction but is still usable. Other plans are to add another room. Other then that, this home is fully functional and is put together very good. The lighting is nice, the look and feel isn\'t over the top like so many other player homes out there. I will add updates for this home as I go. Followers, servants ect ect.

Check out my other mods, please endorse and send me feedback.
author: Revamped

files.name: Kyneview Manor
files.changelogHtml:
Now added to the map.
Added a grindstone to the workshop. The movers lost my good one, go figure.
Added magic special effects to the main teleport stone and the stone in the house.
Fixed a small gap in the stairs.
Replaced the text on the teleport stones that read Teleport to Home, it now reads Teleport to Kyneview Manor.
If you have already have a version of 1.0 and want to switch over to 1.2, don't forget to clear out all your items !
